		<h3>o pali e nasin ilo pi lipu ni</h3>
		<p>sina pali ilo li lukin e pakala la o kama pona e pakala. kulupu li pali lon poki kepeken <a href="https://github.com/pona-la/tokipona.net">ilo Kita</a>. nasin ilo la mi wile e pali pi nasin tu:</p>
		<p><strong>nasin pi pona pilin</strong>. jan li kepeken lipu la jan o pilin pona o kama ala pilin utala pi sona ala tan ni: nasin ilo li nasa.</p>
		<p><strong>nasin pi ken mute</strong>. jan mute o ken lukin e lipu kepeken ilo pi nasin ante mute. jan li ken ala lukin li ken kute taso e lipu la ona kin o ken kepeken lipu. sina lukin e pakala lon nasin ni. </p>
		<p><strong>nasin pi lili wawa</strong>. ilo o ken kepeken tenpo lili o kama ala moli tan ni: toki Sawaki mute li alasa namako e lipu.</p>
